<backend-requirements>
- Python 3.12.8
- FastAPI-based Python service
- Static typing enforced by MyPY - stick to static definitions on all generations
- Avoid untyped dictionaries and prefer pydantic.BaseModel
- Follow strict type annotations throughout the codebase
</backend-requirements>

<core-components>
- `main.py`: Application entry point
- `routes.py`: API endpoints
- `query_agent_service.py`: Main method for launching the data query agent
</core-components>

<coding-standards>
- Use pydantic.BaseModel for data validation and serialization
- Ensure all functions have proper type hints
- Follow FastAPI best practices for async/await patterns
- Maintain clean separation between routes, services, and data models
</coding-standards>
